    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. so if I have a lot of stuff just sitting in the back room not moving, how do I figure out if it's actually a problem or just a seasonal thing? like, what are some specific signs that my stock management is actually failing vs just being slow?",
      "source": "evaluator",
